<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
  <style>
    body {
      font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
      line-height: 1.6;
    }
    .container {
      max-width: 600px;
      margin: 0 auto;
      padding: 20px;
      border: 1px solid #ddd;
      border-radius: 8px;
    }
    .header {
      font-size: 18px;
      font-weight: bold;
      color: #333;
    }
    .footer {
      font-size: 12px;
      color: #666;
      margin-top: 20px;
    }
  </style>
</head>
<body>
  <div class="container">
    <div class="header">
      Hello <%= @student.name %>,
    </div>
    <p>
      Your quiz "<strong><%= @quiz.title %></strong>" has been marked by your teacher. Please visit the submission page on the website to view the results.
    </p>
    <h3>Feedback Highlights:</h3>
    <% @quiz.questions.each do |question| %>
      <p><b>Question <%= question.id %>: </b><%= question.answers.where(student_id: @student.id).last&.mark&.comment.blank? ? "No comment." : question.answers.where(student_id: @student.id).last&.mark&.comment %></p>
    <% end %>
    <p>
      Keep up the great work, and let us know if you have any questions.
    </p>
    <p>Best regards,</p>
    <p>The Koi Viva Voce Team</p>
    <div class="footer">
      This is an automated message. Please do not reply directly to this email.
    </div>
  </div>
</body>
</html>
